Non-Interactive Simulation

A Non Interactive Simulation will be configured by a noninteractive session setting and an initial model
After Starting a non interactive simulation the choosen setting will be used to modify the init.txt
and the runtime will be executed.

Pre-Condition:
	P1. A Simulation project and a corresponding Simulation session configuration had been chosen
	P2. Simulation Runtime has been prepared and is running
	P3. Change Perspective to Simulation Perspective

Post-Condition:
	Post1. Close Non Interactive Simulation Perspective/Views to avoid nullpointexception

1. Simulation Center

2. Simulation Session Control
	2.1 Add a visualization wizard
		o Properties to be plot on display (Dialog mit check box aller verfügbaren properties)
	2.2 Delte, ...
	
3. Simulation Property Control
	3.1 Manuelle eingabe des wertes
	3.2 Slider zum ändern das wertes
	
4. Simulation Visualization
	4.1 anzeigen der Werte in einem fortlaufenden Intervall fenster
	4.2 anzeigen aller werte aber nur als snapshot beim anklicken!?

